datasets.name: dataset_5
queryLines: SELECT Screen AS Screen, DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', Event_Date_Time) AS Monthly_Event_Date, MEASURE(Unique_Screen_Views) AS Unique_Screen_Views FROM hpx_events_model WHERE Event_Date_Time >= '2023-05-01' AND Screen NOT IN ('home', 'welcome', 'welcomecontainer', 'welcome-core', 'support') AND Ui_Action = 'screendisplayed' GROUP BY Screen, DATE_TRUNC('MONTH', Event_Date_Time) ORDER BY Monthly_Event_Date

frame.title: Top Unique Screen Views by Screen
